  <v-dialog

import imgMockup from '../assets/scene00001.png'
export default {
    name: 'ImageGallery',
    props: {
      showDialog: {
        type: Boolean,
        required: true,
      }
    },
    data() {
      return {
        imgs: imgMockup,
        icons:{
          closeWindow: 'mdi-window-close'
        },
      }

    computed:{
      getShow(){
        let localShow = this.showDialog
        return localShow
      }
    },
    methods: {
      closeGallery(){
        this.$emit('closeGallery',false)
      }
    },
    
}
</script>
